{
    "product": {
        "id": 8388223238294,
        "title": "iPhone 12 128GB",
        "body_html": "\u003cstyle type=\"text\/css\"\u003e\u003c!--\ntd {border: 1px solid #cccccc;}br {mso-data-placement:same-cell;}\n--\u003e\u003c\/style\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-sheets-root=\"1\" data-sheets-value=\"{\u0026quot;1\u0026quot;:2,\u0026quot;2\u0026quot;:\u0026quot;The iPhone 12 128GB features a 6.1-inch Super Retina XDR OLED display, offering a significant improvement in brightness and color accuracy over the previous LCD models. Under the hood, it's powered by Apple's A14 Bionic chip, which brings enhanced performance and efficiency. \\n\\nThe iPhone 12 128GB boasts a dual-camera system with 12 MP wide and ultra-wide lenses, featuring Night mode on both cameras, Deep Fusion, and Smart HDR 3 for superior photo quality.\\n\\nIn design, the iPhone 12 128GB marks a return to the flat-edge aesthetic reminiscent of the iPhone 4, encased in an aerospace-grade aluminum frame and Ceramic Shield front cover for improved durability. It supports 5G connectivity, MagSafe technology for wireless charging and accessory attachment, and is IP68 rated for water and dust resistance. \\n\\nOur refurbished iPhone 12 128GB device has undergone our 72-point Blancco test to ensure 100% quality and peace of mind, and only has genuine manufacturer parts. As a standard, all of our refurbished mobiles come with a 12-month warranty.\u0026quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat='{\"2\":897,\"3\":{\"1\":0},\"10\":0,\"11\":4,\"12\":0}'\u003eThe iPhone 12 128GB features a 6.1-inch Super Retina XDR OLED display, offering a significant improvement in brightness and color accuracy over the previous LCD models. Under the hood, it's powered by Apple's A14 Bionic chip, which brings enhanced performance and efficiency. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eThe iPhone 12 128GB boasts a dual-camera system with 12 MP wide and ultra-wide lenses, featuring Night mode on both cameras, Deep Fusion, and Smart HDR 3 for superior photo quality.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eIn design, the iPhone 12 128GB marks a return to the flat-edge aesthetic reminiscent of the iPhone 4, encased in an aerospace-grade aluminum frame and Ceramic Shield front cover for improved durability. It supports 5G connectivity, MagSafe technology for wireless charging and accessory attachment, and is IP68 rated for water and dust resistance. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eOur refurbished iPhone 12 128GB device has undergone our 72-point Phonecheck test to ensure 100% quality and peace of mind, and only has genuine manufacturer parts. As a standard, all of our refurbished mobiles come with a 12-month warranty.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e",
